 d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col bg-black text-white font-sans selection:bg-purple-500/30\"><section class=\"min-h-[100vh] flex flex-col justify-center px-6 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550745165-9bc0b252726f?q=80&amp;w=2000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Abstract Tech\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 mix-blend-luminosity\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black via-black/80 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50px)\"><div class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-300 text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-8\">Arasue Media</div><h1 class=\"text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[10rem] font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-[0.85] bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-white/40\">Shaping Digital Culture</h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-3xl mt-12 max-w-2xl font-light opacity-80 leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-6\">Arasue Media is a powerhouse of content creation, streaming, and digital storytelling.</p><div class=\"pt-16 flex flex-wrap gap-6\"><button class=\"px-10 py-5 rounded-full bg-white text-black font-black text-lg hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all uppercase tracking-wide\">Watch Latest</button><button class=\"px-10 py-5 rounded-full border-2 border-white/20 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 active:scale-95 transition-all uppercase tracking-wide\">Partner with Us</button></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 border-y border-white/10 bg-white/5 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex gap-16 items-center whitespace-nowrap opacity-50 font-bold text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest\"><span>NETFLIX</span> • <span>HBO MAX</span> • <span>TWITCH</span> • <span>YOUTUBE</span> • <span>SPOTIFY</span> • <span>RED BULL</span> •<span>NETFLIX</span> • <span>HBO MAX</span> • <span>TWITCH</span> • <span>YOUTUBE</span> • <span>SPOTIFY</span> • <span>RED BULL</span></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8\"><div><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4\">Selected Campaigns</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-white/50 max-w-sm hidden md:block\">A glimpse into the cultural moments we&#x27;ve manufactured for global brands.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors bg-purple-500 text-white\">All</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors bg-white/5 text-white/50 hover:bg-white/10\">Twitch</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors bg-white/5 text-white/50 hover:bg-white/10\">TikTok</button><button class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors bg-white/5 text-white/50 hover:bg-white/10\">YouTube</button></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"group cursor-pointer relative aspect-video bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542204165-65bf26472b9b?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Energy Rush Live\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/20 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-xs\">4.2M<!-- --> Impressions</div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 md:p-12 w-full translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500\"><div class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-3 uppercase\">Red Bull<!-- --> • <!-- -->Twitch</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase\">Energy Rush Live</h3></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer relative aspect-video bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552566626-52f8b828add9?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Sneaker Drop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/20 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-xs\">12M<!-- --> Impressions</div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 md:p-12 w-full translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500\"><div class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-3 uppercase\">Nike<!-- --> • <!-- -->TikTok</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase\">Sneaker Drop</h3></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer relative aspect-video bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498049794561-7780e7231661?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Tech Unboxing\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/20 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-xs\">8.5M<!-- --> Impressions</div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 md:p-12 w-full translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500\"><div class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-3 uppercase\">Sony<!-- --> • <!-- -->YouTube</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase\">Tech Unboxing</h3></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer relative aspect-video bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514525253161-7a46d19cd819?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Summer Fest\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/20 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-xs\">22M<!-- --> Impressions</div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 md:p-12 w-full translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500\"><div class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm mb-3 uppercase\">Spotify<!-- --> • <!-- -->TikTok</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase\">Summer Fest</h3></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6 bg-white text-black\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-16 uppercase\">Our Capabilities</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"aspect-square bg-black text-white p-10 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-end group cursor-pointer relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-10 right-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\">🎥</div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight\">Content Production</h3></div><div class=\"aspect-square bg-black/5 p-10 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-end group cursor-pointer relative overflow-hidden hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-10 right-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\">🔴</div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight\">Live Streaming</h3></div><div class=\"aspect-square bg-black/5 p-10 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-end group cursor-pointer relative overflow-hidden hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-10 right-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\">✨</div><h3 class=\"text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight\">Digital Branding</h3></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6 border-y border-white/10 bg-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-24\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6\">Campaign Architecture</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-white/50 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">How we manufacture virality, predictably.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-purple-500/20 transition-colors mb-4\">01</div><div class=\"border-t border-white/20 pt-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-4\">Data &amp; Cultural Anthropology</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">We don&#x27;t guess. We analyze deep cultural trends and platform algorithms to find the white space for your brand.</p></div></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-purple-500/20 transition-colors mb-4\">02</div><div class=\"border-t border-white/20 pt-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-4\">Creator Casting</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Matching your brand not just with follower counts, but with creators who have genuine, cult-like influence over your target demographic.</p></div></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-purple-500/20 transition-colors mb-4\">03</div><div class=\"border-t border-white/20 pt-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-4\">Content Engineering</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Producing high-retention, platform-native content that feels organic, not like an ad.</p></div></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-purple-500/20 transition-colors mb-4\">04</div><div class=\"border-t border-white/20 pt-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-4\">Amplification</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">Using paid media to pour gasoline on the organic fire, maximizing ROI and driving measurable conversions.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6\">The Roster</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-white/50 mb-16\">Our exclusive network of digital talent and producers.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"group cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&amp;w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;sig=1\" alt=\"Creator 1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><div class=\"font-bold\">@creator<!-- -->1</div><div class=\"text-sm text-purple-400\">1.<!-- -->1<!-- -->M Followers</div></div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&amp;w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;sig=2\" alt=\"Creator 2\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><div class=\"font-bold\">@creator<!-- -->2</div><div class=\"text-sm text-purple-400\">1.<!-- -->2<!-- -->M Followers</div></div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&amp;w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;sig=3\" alt=\"Creator 3\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><div class=\"font-bold\">@creator<!-- -->3</div><div class=\"text-sm text-purple-400\">1.<!-- -->3<!-- -->M Followers</div></div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-white/5 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mb-6 relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&amp;w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;sig=4\" alt=\"Creator 4\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><div class=\"font-bold\">@creator<!-- -->4</div><div class=\"text-sm text-purple-400\">1.<!-- -->4<!-- -->M Followers</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"flex-1 p-8 lg:p-12\"><div class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black uppercase mb-2\">Campaign ROI Estimator</h2><p class=\"text-white/50\">Project your potential reach and conversions based on your influencer marketing budget.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-4\"><label class=\"font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-purple-400\">Campaign Budget</label><span class=\"font-mono text-white/80\">$10,000 USD</span></div><input type=\"range\" min=\"5000\" max=\"200000\" step=\"1000\" class=\"w-full accent-purple-500 h-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full appearance-none cursor-pointer\" value=\"10000\"/></div><div><label class=\"font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-purple-400 block mb-6\">Primary Platform</label><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><button class=\"py-4 px-6 rounded-xl border text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 text-left border-purple-500 bg-purple-500/20 text-white\">TikTok (Viral Reach)</button><button class=\"py-4 px-6 rounded-xl border text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 text-left border-white/10 text-white/50 hover:border-white/30\">YouTube (Deep Conversion)</button><button class=\"py-4 px-6 rounded-xl border text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 text-left border-white/10 text-white/50 hover:border-white/30\">Twitch (Live Engagement)</button></div></div></div></div><div class=\"md:w-[400px] bg-purple-900/20 border-l border-white/10 p-8 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"space-y-8 mb-8 transition-all duration-200 blur-0 opacity-100\"><div><h3 class=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs text-white/50 mb-2\">Estimated Reach</h3><div class=\"text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white\">1.5M+</div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs text-white/50 mb-2\">Est. Conversions</h3><div class=\"text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-purple-400\">7,500</div></div></div><p class=\"text-white/40 text-xs mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium\">*Projections based on historical aggregate data. Actual results depend on creative execution and product-market fit.</p><button class=\"w-full bg-white text-black font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-sm py-5 rounded-xl hover:bg-neutral-200 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(168,85,247,0.3)]\">Discuss Strategy</button></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6 border-t border-white/10 text-center\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8\">Collaborate</h2><p class=\"text-2xl text-white/60 mb-12\">Ready to go viral? Let&#x27;s talk strategy.</p><button class=\"px-12 py-6 rounded-full bg-purple-600 text-white font-black text-xl hover:bg-purple-500 active:scale-95 transition-all uppercase tracking-wide shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(147,51,234,0.3)]\">Send Brief</button></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/33jtdm1y108jx.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n7:\